quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Twaa, Sin, Mim."
  26,2,"Tsino ni tsinyaali tsia Eshitabu shinoosinjia."
  26,3,"Khaundi onyala okhwiyira shichila mbu shibaba Abasuubili tawe."
  26,4,"Ne khwenyanga, khwakhabeshilie eshimanyisio okhurula hekulu, mana amakosi kabu katong’e nikashihotselesilie."
  26,5,"Ne shibuboolelanga obwitsulisio obuyiakha okhurula khu Omunji wetsimbabaasi tawe, halali beretsanga ehale ninabo."
  26,6,"Toto bo bamala okhuyingasia, kho laano ahambi hano balanyoola amacheni kakalia kabakholelanga emibayo."
  26,7,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo liloba tawe, ni emimela chinga chia khwamesiamwo, chia buli imbia indayi?"
  26,8,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shinibokhusuubila tawe."
  26,9,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,10,"Ne olwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yalaanga Musa, namuboolela mbu: “Tsia khubandu balia abamabii."
  26,11,"Abandu ba Firauni. Koo, shibaritsanga Nyasaye tawe?”"
  26,12,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, esie eritsanga baletsa okhungatsula tawe."
  26,13,"Ne eshilifu shianje shilola obusiro, ne olulimi lwanje shilurumbulanga obulayi tawe. Kho, yilila oburume (buno) khu Haruni (yesi)."
  26,14,"Nabo bali nende likhobo khwisie, kho eritsanga mbu balanzira.”"
  26,15,"Naboola mbu: “Shikali kario tawe. Kho tsie nende ebimanyisio biefu. Toto efwe khuli halala ninanyu, khuwulilanga."
  26,16,"Kho tsie khu Firauni mana mumuboolele mbu: ‘Toto efwe khuli Abarumwa ba Nyasaye webiloonje bioosi."
  26,17,"Mbu olekhule halala ninafu Abana ba Israili.’”"
  26,18,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, shikhwakhulelela ewefu noli omwana, ne niwikhala mwifwe emika mulubaka lulwo?"
  26,19,"Ne nokhola eshikhole shishio shilia shawakhola, ne noba mubalia abalakhupanga orio tawe.”"
  26,20,"(Musa) naboola mbu: “Ndakhola ako olwa ndali nendi mubandu balia abakora."
  26,21,"Mana nebelukha olwa ndali nebarire, ne Nyasaye wanje Omulesi niyambelesia obwami, ne niyakhola okhuba Mubarumwa."
  26,22,"Ne echo nicho emikabo chiawumborolelangakhwo echia wakholela, ne wara Abana ba Israili mubusandi.”"
  26,23,"Firauni naboola mbu: “Ne Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi oyo ni wina?”"
  26,24,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye Omulesi owaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio, toto nimuli abokhusuubila nobwatoto.”"
  26,25,"(Firauni) Naboolela balia abali nibamubotokhane mumbeka wuwe mbu: “Koo, shimuwulilanga tawe?”"
  26,26,"(Musa) naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi nende Nyasaye Omulesi wa bapapa benyu abaranjilila.”"
  26,27,"(Firauni) naboola mbu: “Toto bwene Omurumwa wenyu owamwarumilwa ni omulalu.”"
  26,28,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Niye Nyasaye Omulesi wa Ebukwe nende Mumbo nende ebili hakari wabio, toto enywe nimuli mbu mwikhonyelanga obwongo.”"
  26,29,"(Firauni) naboola mbu: “Niwitsa okhusuubila nyasaye wundi ulali esie tawe, toto nditsa okhukhukhola obe mubaboye.”"
  26,30,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, kata nekhurerera eshindu shili mubwang’angu?”"
  26,31,"Naboola mbu: “Nakhashirerakhwo, toto noli mubandu baboolanga obwatoto.”"
  26,32,"Mana nasukuna hasi indabushi yiyie, lola, niikalukhana inzukha ilolekha."
  26,33,"Ne narusia omukhono kukwe, lola, nikuba omulafu tswe khubahenganga."
  26,34,"(Firauni) naboolela abakhongo bali nibamubotokhane mbu: “Toto uno ni omulosi umanyile muno."
  26,35,"Yenyanga okhubarusia mushialo shienyu nende obulosi bubwe, kho muboola murie?”"
  26,36,"Nibaboola mbu: “Mhelesie ebise ye nende omusiani wabu, ne orume mumatokho abandu bakhung’asinjia Abandu."
  26,37,"Balakhurerera buli omulosi omukhongo umanyile muno.”"
  26,38,"Kho, abalosi abo nibakhung’asibwa khulwa ebise nende inyanga imanyikhane."
  26,39,"Ne Abandu nibaboolelwa mbu: “Mumalile okhukhung’ana?"
  26,40,"Khaundi khunyala okhuloonda abalosi nikali mbu nibo nibalashila.”"
  26,41,"Kho mana abalosi shingala boola, nibaboolela Firauni mbu: “Koo, khulanyoola omurungo nikaba mbu nefwe khushila?”"
  26,42,"Naboola mbu: “Eeh, ne khandi mwitsa okhuba mubalia abalarebwa hambi.”"
  26,43,"Musa nababoolela mbu: “Sukune ebiamwenya okhusukuna.”"
  26,44,"Nibasukuna emikoye chiabu nende tsindabushi tsiabu, ne nibaboola mbu: “Khumaani ka Firauni efwe sa toto nefwe khulashila.”"
  26,45,"Mana Musa nasukuna indabushi yiyie, mana niimilaa bioosi biabachikhanga."
  26,46,"Awo abalosi nibakwa hasi, nibara hasi obweni bwabu (nibasujuda)."
  26,47,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khusuubile Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,48,"Nyasaye Omulesi wa Musa nende Haruni.”"
  26,49,"(Firauni) naboola mbu: “Mumusuubile neshili okhubasubula. Toto ye niye Omukhongo wenyu owabechesia obulosi. Kho, mwitsa okhulola. Nditsa toto okhuteta emikhono chienyu nende ebilenje bienyu buchikha, ne toto nditsa okhubabamba mwesi.”"
  26,50,"Nibaboola mbu: “Obubii bubulaho tawe. Toto efwe khwitsa okhukalukha khu Nyasaye wefu Omulesi."
  26,51,"Toto efwe khusuubile mbu Nyasaye wefu Omulesi alakhuleshela tsimbi tsiefu shichila efwe khubeele bokhuranjilila okhusuubila.”"
  26,52,"Ne nikhufimbulila Musa mbu: “Rula nende abandu banje ebise bieshilo, toto enywe mwitsa okhulondwakho.”"
  26,53,"Mana Firauni naruma abakhung’asinjia abandu mumatokho."
  26,54,"""Toto bano ni omukanda omutiti."
  26,55,"Nabo toto bakhusinyisinjia muno."
  26,56,"Nafu toto khuli abanji, ne khukholele koosi kookhukhula efwe khubashile.”"
  26,57,"Mana nikhubarusia mumikunda nende tsisebele."
  26,58,"Nende emiandu emisirosiro nende habundu andayi."
  26,59,"Ne endio, mana nikhuchelamia ebio Abana ba Israili."
  26,60,"Mana olwa eliuba liarula itsuli, nibabalondakhwo."
  26,61,"Ne olwa emikanda chibili echo chialolana, Abandu ba Musa nibaboola mbu: “Toto efwe khutililwe.”"
  26,62,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Shikali kario tawe. Toto Nyasaye wanje Omulesi ali halala ninasi, yetsa okhulunjisia.”"
  26,63,"Mana nikhufimbulila Musa mbu: “Khupa indabushi yiyio khu inyanza.” Mana niikabukhana, ne buli elubeka niba shinga olukulu olukhongo."
  26,64,"Mana nikhusitia hambi hao Abandu bandi abo."
  26,65,"Mana nikhuhonokosia Musa nende balia abali halala ninaye boosi."
  26,66,"Mana nikhusishilia mumatsi abandi abo."
  26,67,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibasuubilanga tawe."
  26,68,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,69,"Ne basomele amakhuwa ka Ibrahim."
  26,70,"Olwa yaboolela papa wuwe nende Abandu bebe mbu: “Shina shiamulaamanga?”"
  26,71,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khulaamanga ebifwanani, mana khutong’e hao tsinyanga tsiosi (khubilamanga).”"
  26,72,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, bibawulilanga olwa mubilaanganga?"
  26,73,"Nohomba bibakhonyangakhwo (nimubilaama), nohomba bibawumisinjia (nimukhaya okhubilama)?"""
  26,74,"Nibaboola mbu: “(Shibikholanga ako tawe) halali khwanyoola bapapa befu nibakholanga bario.”"
  26,75,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, mulolanga ebia mulaamanga ebo?"
  26,76,"Enywe nende abakofu benyu abaranjilila?"
  26,77,"Toto abo ni abasuku banje (abamulaamanga abo) halali Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,78,"Ulia owanoonga, naye niye ulunjisinjia."
  26,79,"Ne niye undisinjia khandi unywesinjia."
  26,80,"Ne nendwala, niye umboninjia."
  26,81,"Ne niye ulifwisia ne alilamusia."
  26,82,"Ne niye wesuubilanga mbu alindeshela ebionono bianje inyanga yomurungo."
  26,83,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesia amachesi kokhukhalaka eshina ne unde halala nende abakholi bamalayi."
  26,84,"Ne ukhole embe wokhuboolwa khubulayi nende Abandu balitsa inyuma."
  26,85,"Ne ukhole embe mu balichelama omukunda kwomwikulu kwobwokholo."
  26,86,"Ne oleshele papa wanje. Toto ye yali mubandu bakora."
  26,87,"Ne olanzafia tsisoni tawe inyanga yabalilamusibwa."
  26,88,"Inyanga yoomwandu nohomba abana shibilikhoonya shiosishiosi tawe."
  26,89,"Halali ulia wulitsia khu Nyasaye nende omwoyo omulafu."""
  26,90,"Ne omukunda kwomwikulu kulisitibwa hambi nende balia baria Nyasaye."
  26,91,"Ne Jahanam ililolosibwa khubandu ababii."
  26,92,"Ne baliboolelwa mbu: “Bali hena balia abamwalaamanga?"
  26,93,"Abalali Nyasaye tawe. Koo, banyala okhubakhonya nohomba bekhonye abeene?”"
  26,94,"Kho balisukunwa omo, bo nende abakori bandi."
  26,95,"Nende omukanda kwa Ibilisi kwoosi."
  26,96,"Baliboola nibasolanangamwo mbu:"
  26,97,"“Khwitsuba khu Nyasaye, toto efwe khwali mubukori bwa habulafu."
  26,98,"Olwa khwabakholanga enywe okhuba nashilala nende Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,99,"Ne shibakhukosia tawe halali Abamabii."
  26,100,"Kholano khubula abakhusabila tawe."
  26,101,"Nohomba omwitsa owatoto."
  26,102,"Abayie khunyalanga okhukalukha, khwakhabeele mubasuubili batoto.”"
  26,103,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko, ne abanji mubo shinibokhusuubila tawe."
  26,104,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,105,"Abandu ba Nuhu, bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,106,"Olwa Omusiani wabu (ulangwa mbu) Nuhu yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimularia Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,107,"Toto esie khwinywe endi Omurumwa Omwisikwa."
  26,108,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,109,"Ne shebasabanga khu kano omurungo kwosikwosi tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli butswa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi."
  26,110,"Kho, rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie.”"
  26,111,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khukhusuubile ewe ne ni abandu abateshele nibo bakhuloondanga?”"
  26,112,"Naboola mbu: “Emanyiile shina kalia akabakholanga?"
  26,113,"Ne okhubalilwa ebikhole khwabu khuli butswa khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, abayie mumanyangakhwo."
  26,114,"Ne esie shinditsa okhulonda Abasuubili batsie ehale tawe."
  26,115,"Esie shendi shiosishiosi tawe halali omwikanyilisi owa habulafu.”"
  26,116,"Nibaboola mbu: “Nolalekhana ninaafu tawe ewe Nuhu, toto olaba mubalia balalaswa amachina.”"
  26,117,"Nuhu naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto Abandu banje bayingasiye."
  26,118,"Kho, khalaka eshina hakari wanje ninabo okhukhalaka okhulayi, ne uhabine esie nende balia bali halala ninasi mubasuubili.”"
  26,119,"Kho mana nikhumuhabina ye nende balia bali halala ninaye musafina yitsule."
  26,120,"Mana okhurula awo, nikhusishia balia abatong’a."
  26,121,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko, halali abaanji mubo shibali bokhusuubila tawe."
  26,122,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,123,"Babu A’di boosi bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,124,"(Betsulisie) Olwa Omusiani wabu, Hud yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimularia Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,125,"Toto esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa omwisikwa."
  26,126,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,127,"Ne shebasabanga khu kano omurungo kwosikwosi tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,128,"Koo, mumbakhanga buli khwitulo, eshitsulisio shiokhukhola kalia kabulamwo oluchendo."
  26,129,"Ne mumbakhanga tsingoba mpara mbu mulimenya tsinyanga tsioosi?"
  26,130,"Ne nimusera, museranga nobufuru."
  26,131,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile."
  26,132,"Ne rie ulia owabahelesia kalia akamumanyile."
  26,133,"Yabahelesia emiruko nende Abana abasiani."
  26,134,"Nende emikunda nende tsisebele."
  26,135,"Toto ebaririranga eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo.”"
  26,136,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ni nashilala butswa khwifwe, nokhuchelela nohomba noobula okhukhuchelela."
  26,137,"Kano shikali sa halali ebima biabandu bakhale."
  26,138,"Ne efwe shikhulihebwa eshinyasio tawe.”"
  26,139,"Mana nibamuyingasia, ne nikhubasishia. Toto mu kano kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibali Abasuubili tawe."
  26,140,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,141,"Babu Thamudi bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,142,"Olwa Omusiani wabu ulangwa mbu Swaleh yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimuritsanga Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,143,"Toto esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa omwisikwa."
  26,144,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,145,"Ne shiebeenyakhwo omurungo khu kano tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi."
  26,146,"Koo, mulalekhwa nomulembe khu kali hano kano?"
  26,147,"Mumikunda nende tsisebele."
  26,148,"Nende emimela nende mitende chia ebibuli bienga."
  26,149,"Ne muyabanga mutsingulu tsinzu mukhwisangasia butswa."
  26,150,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,151,"Ne mulaloonda amalako ka ababuririranga eshichelo tawe."
  26,152,"Balia bakholanga obwonooni khushialo, ne shibakasinjia tawe.”"
  26,153,"Nibaboola mbu: “Toto ewe oli mubalia abalokwa."
  26,154,"Ewe sholi shiosishiosi tawe halali omundu butswa shinga efwe. Kho rerakhwo eshimanyisio nikakhaba mbu oboolanga obwatoto.”"
  26,155,"Naboola mbu: “Ingamia ikhasi njieino, ibe nende ebise biayo biokhunywa, nanyu mwesi mube nende ebise ebimanyishe biokhunywa."
  26,156,"Ne mulayitilakhwo khububii tawe, eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo shiaboolela.”"
  26,157,"Halali bo nibayiira, mana nibaba bokhwiyitsulisia."
  26,158,"Mana eshinyasio nishibeshela. Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibasuubila tawe."
  26,159,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye owa Amaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,160,"Abandu ba Luti bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,161,"Olwa Omusiani wabu (ulangwa mbu) Luti yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimuritsanga tawe?"
  26,162,"Toto esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa omwisikwa."
  26,163,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,164,"Ne shindenyakhwo omurungo khu kano tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,165,"Koo, mubiloonje bioosi mukholanga eshifwolo abasaatsa khubasatsa?"
  26,166,"Ne mulekhanga shia Nyasaye wenyu yabaloonjela khubakhasi benyu? Toto enywe muli abandu babura eshichelo.”"
  26,167,"Baboola mbu: “Ewe Lut, nolalekhana ninafu tawe, olaba mubalia abalatafibwa.”"
  26,168,"Naboola mbu: “Esie toto endi mubasinyisibwa muno nende eshikhole shienyu esho."""
  26,169,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, habina esie nende Abandu banje okhurulana nende akabakholanga kano."""
  26,170,"Mana nikhumuhabina ye nende Abandu bebe boosi."
  26,171,"Halali Omushiele khubalia abekhalanga inyuma."
  26,172,"Mana nikhusishia abandi abo."
  26,173,"Mana nikhubakwisilia ifula, ne ni ifula imbii muno ya balia bekanyilisibwa."
  26,174,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko, halali abaanji mubo shibasuubilanga tawe."
  26,175,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,176,"Abandu bomutsuru omukhongo bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,177,"Olwa Shuwaib yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimuritsangakhwo Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,178,"Toto Esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa Omwisikwa."
  26,179,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,180,"Ne shebasabaanga khu kano omurungo kwosikwosi tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,181,"Itsusie eshichelo obulayi, ne mulaba mubalia baleeminjia tawe."
  26,182,"Ne chele khushichelo shili habwene."
  26,183,"Ne mulaleemilia Abandu ebindu biabu tawe, ne mulachenda khushialo nimukhola obwonooni tawe."
  26,184,"Ne rie owabaloonga enywe nende ebiloonje biabura bioosi."""
  26,185,"Baboola mbu: “Toto ewe oli mubalia abalokwa."
  26,186,"Newe sholi shiosishiosi tawe halali omundu sa shinga efwe, ne toto efwe khukhulola mbu oli mubabeyi."
  26,187,"Kho mana khukwisilie ebitonye bia likulu toto noli mubalia baboolanga obwatieli.”"
  26,188,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi amanyile muno akamukholanga.”"
  26,189,"Mana nibamuyingasia, ne eshinyasio shieyinyanga yeshinikha nishiboolela. Toto esho shali eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo."
  26,190,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibali bokhusuubila tawe."
  26,191,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,192,"Ne toto obo ni obwishio bwa Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,193,"Yekha nabwo Roho omwisikwa."
  26,194,"Khu mwoyo kukwo, kho obe mubalia abekanyilisinjia."
  26,195,"Mulusungo lwa olwarabu lwa habulafu."
  26,196,"Ne toto kano kali mubitabu ebiaranjilila."
  26,197,"Koo, shishiali eshimanyisio khubo tawe mbu kano bakamanya abasomi ba Abana ba Israili?"
  26,198,"Ne khushishinjia khu ulia ulali omwarabu tawe."
  26,199,"Mana abasoomele, shibakhamusuubile tawe."
  26,200,"Ne endi nilwa khwinjisinjia (okhukatsula) mumioyo chia ababii."
  26,201,"Shibayisuubilanga tawe okhula shingala balola eshinyasio eshilulu."
  26,202,"Mana shibetsele mapwoka, nabo nibalamanyile tawe."
  26,203,"Mana baboole mbu: “Koo, efwe khulahebwa ebise?”"
  26,204,"Mana koo, bayungubalilanga eshinyasio shiefu?"
  26,205,"Olola orie nikhubamenyia obulayi emika eminji."
  26,206,"Mana kabanyoole kalia akabalakungwa."
  26,207,"Kalibakhonya shina amalayi kabamenyibwamo?"
  26,208,"Ne sikhwasishia olukongo lwosilwosi tawe nikhushili okhurumamwo Abekanyilisi."
  26,209,"(Kho bibe) obwitsulisio, ne shikhwali abakhola obubii tawe."
  26,210,"Ne Amashetani shikekha nayo tawe."
  26,211,"Ne shikakhoyeshele tawe, ne shikakhanyala tawe."
  26,212,"Toto abo bekalilwa okhuwulila."
  26,213,"Kho olalaama halala nende Nyasaye abanyasaye bandi tawe, wakhetsa waba mubalia balinyoola eshinyasio."
  26,214,"Ne wikanyilisie Abandu bobo ba ahambi."
  26,215,"Ne ore hasi olubaha lulwo khu ulia ukhuloonda mubasuubili."
  26,216,"Ne nibalakhuwulila tawe, boola mbu: “Esie ndiira ehale muno nende akamukholanga.”"
  26,217,"Ne wisiche ulia owa Amaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,218,"Ulia ukhulolanga olwa wemanga."
  26,219,"Nende okhukalukhana khukhwo mubasujudanga."
  26,220,"Toto Ye niye Omuwulili po, Omumanyi muno."
  26,221,"Koo, ebaboolelekhwo ni wina wamashetani keshelangakhwo?"
  26,222,"Keshelanga buli omuchishi omukhongo, omunji wetsimbi."
  26,223,"Kabayililanga kalia akakaulilanga, ne abaanji mubo nababeyi."
  26,224,"Ne abembanga amashairi nibo ababakori balondangakhwo."
  26,225,"Koo, shololanga mbu bo bayiyayiyanga buli mwitwoma tawe?"
  26,226,"Ne mbu bo baboolanga akabalakholanga tawe?"
  26,227,"Halali balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, mana nibetsulila Nyasaye muno, mana nibashila olunyuma lwa okhukholelwa obubii. Ne balia abakholanga obubii bakhamanye mbu ni omukalukho kuli kurie kwabalikalukha."
